{
  "stem": "21550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes, you just thought of a name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- and-- and it's-- it's-- it's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the war, she had a-- angina pectoris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a very bad heart condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before the war, she wouldn't-- she-- she shouldn't have bent down it was so bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, she was carrying those big heads of cabbage and potatoes, which we ate a lot of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but she-- she spent a few nights sitting on-- in strange courtyards, spending the night, because she didn't have a place to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were, like I said, some Poles who tried to help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one to the other, and she was very diligent, and she worked very hard to get to those people and to persuade them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, this place, this last place where we spent two years, she visited this lady before and asked her, well, she has to give their accommodation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was refused, but not 100%.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, oh, come back in three months, and we'll-- we'll see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It turned out that they had somebody hidden in the house, but they were lured out by the Germans, who through their agent, spread the rumor that if you go to this hotel, and you have $2,000-- and you have to have dollars.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't take any zlotys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For $2,000, you can go to there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can stay in this hotel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we'll take you out into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So a lot of people did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they went straight into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when she came back the second time after three months, those people were gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was willing to take us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, her-- she-- she didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
